                  <dt>Provenance</dt>
          <dd>[E. and A. Silberman Galleries, New York, (by 1939) sold]; to Thomas Mitchell, Los Angeles (1940-1962). [Paul Kantor Gallery, Los Angeles, sold] to William A. Coolidge, gift; to Fogg Art Museum , 1964.<br />
<br />
Notes:<br />
<br />
Silberman suggested that the painting came from a Polish collection.<br />
<br />
</dd>
        
        
        
